    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">328 Mickle Street</name>
                    <name type="place">Camden New Jersey</name>
                    <date when="1884-05-07" rend="right">May 7 '84</date>
                </dateline>
            </opener> 

            <p>Charley, you would do me a special service if you could
                get &#38; send me a good photo (or other picture) of <hi rend="italic">Father
                    Taylor, the old sailor preacher</hi>. I want it to be engraved for a magazine
                    article<ptr target="loc.05771_n1"/>&#8212;Picture will be returned&#8212;also
                find out for me when Father T died&#8212;No particular hurry&#8212;but hope you will
                be able to help me soon as convenient&#8212;</p>
            <p>I have had a bad spell nearly all the year&#8212;till <choice><abbr>ab't</abbr><expan>about</expan></choice> a month ago&#8212;when
                things <choice><abbr>turn'd</abbr><expan>turned</expan></choice> favorably, &#38; I am now about as usual with me&#8212;</p>
<closer>
            <salute>With good old remembrances&#8212;</salute>
            <signed>Walt Whitman</signed>
</closer>
        </body>
    </text>
